entries.femaleVariant: Venture out as often as you can. If you know where to look, it can be beautiful.
Been to cyberspace. What you say's bunk.
Cyberspace "beautiful"? It's a collection of data.
I dunno, seems like bunk. Been to cyberspace. Nothin' special. Minor pixelated nightmare, really.
With many varied and wonderful isles – jungles, mountain valleys, coral reefs...
Old simulacra nestled on uberpowerful servers. One gets a glimpse of what the world once looked like.
If you an' me were to enter the Net right now, it'd tune into our mindsets, offer two different visuals.
But some sites out there, fantastic corners, look the same to us all. Finding those... that's my thing.
